# Quick Test

This repository includes a minimal quick test to verify that the packaged scripts and input data are working correctly.

## Test script

`code/2-Geographical location.py`

## Purpose

This script loads the packaged station CSV file and the U.S. boundary shapefile, then plots the geographic distribution of the study basins.

## How to run

From the repository root:

```bash
cd code
python "2-Geographical location.py"
